WorkItem.Description: Been using Rawr for a while now ... love it!  When I opened it today encountered a strange issue using the ProtWar model.  In the comparison section it only shows the gear I own.  I can't find any setting that would cause such a reaction.  If I change the model to DPSWarr it shows all the gear and when checking items other gear is in the database.  I even created a new file and import and it still only shows my gear.  Creating a new file without importing shows no gear, and again switching to DPSWarr model shows all the gear.  Its driving me nutz ... please help.
WorkItem.Summary: [ProtWarr] No Items displaying other than what is owned. Other models show items

Comments.Message: Could you please provide your char file where this is happening? We'd like to open it as you see it in order to replicate (as my ProtWarr doesn't have this issue).
Here is mine. Note it has been this way since version 2.3.9 and continues through 2.3.11. Individual item lists seem fine, it is just the upgrade list that has issues.
